      • gzip

        public static okhttp3.RequestBody gzip​(okhttp3.RequestBody req,
                                       int compressionLevel)
        origin Returns a gzip version of the RequestBody, with compressed payload. This is not automatic as not all servers support gzip compressed requests.

        ``` val request = Request.Builder().url("...") .addHeader("Content-Encoding", "gzip") .post(uncompressedBody.gzip()) .build() ```
